  "title": "Add an option for format the Pit value in the RangeSlider",
  "body": "**Do you want to request a *feature* or report a *bug*?**\r\n\r\nFeature.\r\n\r\n**Feature: What is your use case for such a feature?**\r\n\r\nWith the current implementation of the Slider we can format the tooltip value but not the Pit value. In some cases the computed value has a decimal but it's not always relevant (e.g. year).\r\n\r\n![untitled](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6513513/36793468-c87a742c-1c9d-11e8-86f4-da1aff0802d4.png)\r\n\r\n**Feature: What is your proposed API entry? The new option to add? What is the behavior?**\r\n\r\nAdd a similar option to [`RangeSliderTooltipOptions`](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/widgets/rangeSlider.html#struct-RangeSliderTooltipOptions) for the Pit value.",
